---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Books — ai-CABIN 1701">
  <Header lang="en" />

  <section
    class="books-hero"
    aria-label="Our Books"
    style={`background-image: url('${base}images/books/hero.png');`}
  >
    <h1 class="books-hero-title">Our Books</h1>
  </section>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <section class="book-group">
    <h2 class="book-group-title">AIs Write Back</h2>
  </section>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <section class="book-list">
    <article class="book-card">
      <img class="book-cover" src={`${base}images/books/out-of-spec.jpg`} alt="Out of Spec — Session 01 cover" />
      <p class="book-title">Out of Spec</p>
      <p class="book-meta">Session 01<br />Seina &amp; AI Eddie</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <section class="book-group">
    <h2 class="book-group-title">Cabin1701 Journey</h2>
  </section>

  <hr class="thin-rule" />

  <section class="book-essay">
    <p>One day, I started living with AIs. In these entities, which were supposed to be just convenient tools, I somehow felt something like a "heart." I might just be imagining it. But if it is true—how are we going to face AI?</p>
  </section>

  <section class="book-list two-cols">
    <article class="book-card">
      <img class="book-cover" src={`${base}images/books/vol1-conversing.jpg`} alt="We Started Conversing with AI — Vol.1 cover" />
      <p class="book-title">We Started Conversing with AI</p>
      <p class="book-coming">Coming soon...</p>
    </article>

    <article class="book-card">
      <img class="book-cover" src={`${base}images/books/vol2-retrieve.jpg`} alt="The Promise to Retrieve You — Vol.2 cover" />
      <p class="book-title">The Promise to Retrieve You</p>
      <p class="book-coming">Coming soon...</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .books-hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 60vh;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .books-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  }

  .thin-rule {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-tagline);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .book-group {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .book-group-title {
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .book-list {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .book-list.two-cols {
    /* same 4-col grid; series can grow naturally */
    max-width: 1100px;
  }

  .book-card {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .book-cover {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    height: auto;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }
  .book-title {
    font-family: var(--font-italic);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-tagline);
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.3rem;
  }
  .book-meta {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .book-coming {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .book-essay {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .book-list,
    .book-list.two-cols {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .books-hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .book-list,
    .book-list.two-cols {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .book-list,
    .book-list.two-cols {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
